          "MONITOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The collimated alpha-particle beam was monitored by",
                "the charge collection method, using Faradays cup,",
                "kept behind the target stack and coupled to a",
                "current integrator."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Targets were made by depositing specpure Pr6O11 of",
                "thickness 5 mg/cm2 on aluminum backing of uniform",
                "thickness 6.75 mg/cm2 by vacuum evaporation technique.",
                "The aluminium backing served as energy degrader for",
                "alpha-particle."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "GELI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " 100 cm3 Ge (Li) detector along with associated",
                "electronics coupled with CANBERA-88 multichannel",
                "analyzer"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "EN-ERR",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Scale error"
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-T",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Total error. The factors likely to introduce",
                "errors in the present measurements and their estimates",
                "are given as:",
                " (i) Targets of different dimensions were weighted on",
                "     an electronic balance and numbers of nuclei",
                "     present in the target were measured. The",
                "     uncertainty in the estimate of number of target",
                "     nuclei is expected to be less than 1 %.",
                " (ii) Error in the fluctuations of the beam current",
                "     has been incorporated by taking the weighted",
                "     average of aplha-paricle beam current and is",
                "     found to be less than 5%.",
                " (iii) The error introduced in the determination",
                "     of the photo-peak area of the characteristic",
                "     gamma-rays were limited within 2-5%.",
                " (iv) The error due to uncertainty in detector",
                "     eft1ciency was estimated to be less than 5%.",
                " (v) The errors due to decrease in beam intensity due",
                "    to scattering while alpha-particle beam traverses",
                "     through the stack is estimared to be less than 1%.",
                " (vi) The inherent uncertainty in the energy of the",
                "     alpha-particle beam, i.e., O.5MeV at 50 MeV",
                "     alpha-particle and the energy spread associated",
                "     with the thickness of each target in the stack",
                "     contributes < 4% to the alpha-particle energy.",
                " (vii) Error associated with the straggling of the",
                "     alpha-particle is estimated to be negligibly small"
              ]
            }
          ],
